{"tid":541840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<普通話，不了！> 中國學生請纓教普通話　促停攻擊浸大","createTime":"2018-01-27T01:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T02:48:54.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8479ba3923ef177a97ac5cc193ba9410a90be0eb","tid":541840,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:24:13.000Z","msg":"內地生請纓教普通話　促停攻擊浸大<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180127/large/a0903a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180127%2Flarge%2Fa0903a.gif&h=8711a25b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地生陳艾嘉　　立場新聞圖片<br />\n【本報訊】浸大去年推出普通話豁免試，合格者可豁免修讀大學的普通話課程。來自上海的中文大學社會學講師黎明於fb專頁分析指，浸大豁免試的口語考核，要求學生懂得代入角色，並須在25分鐘內準備7條短講題，極考驗時間管理，「難度完勝國家統一的普通話水平測試（PSC）」。<br />\n<br />\n講師︰豁免試難過內地試<br />\n<br />\n黎明指出，浸大豁免試要求考生作答的7條短講題目，題目要求短講的長度、角色不一，「不知道的還以為是演藝學院招收表演系學生」。相反，內地的普通話水平測試中口語部份，要求就一個題目說話3分鐘，而「考綱是公開的，考前考生有充份的時間準備所有30則考題」，最終應考時只需2選1作答，評分亦著重語音、語法，主觀的準則如流暢度佔分較少。<br />\n不過，有就讀浸大的內地研究生，卻認為「豁免試比普通話課的期末試難，也是正常的邏輯」。來自深圳的浸大傳理研究生陳艾嘉，在昨日遊行尾聲現身民主牆，張貼「我願意義務幫你輔導普通話，請停止攻擊學校及老師」告示，她接受傳媒訪問時稱普通話現在是國際語言，也是中國官方的語言。香港小學都設有普通話課，「所以大學都應該有的」。<br />\n■記者周 婷<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180127/20286978\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180127%2F20286978&d=iCgR92YlfwCsP0fFg9aSasVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=c18806b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180127%2F20286978&h=b9a6545b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180127/20286978</a>"},{"pid":"916ea9285caaebbc2db0dc384d894d79de5e8e2f","tid":541840,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca84b8f3e5eb17ae631952b506fd83810c4e2d09","tid":541840,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:26:15.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"9e81a011274df459f7e030a6f0e601f06eb136d6","tid":541840,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:36:24.000Z","msg":"香港人講廣東話/英話"},{"pid":"628fabdcbadabab2d31a6840fb8d613f74558475","tid":541840,"uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:41:34.000Z","msg":"不如cut左個蝗語試<br />\n<br />\n我義務教返你粵語啦, 臭八婆！"},{"pid":"0abd4b767fa7bbdc853bc1b4b1e493eecf201ce5","tid":541840,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:42:38.000Z","msg":"推普廢粵<br />\n不了！"},{"pid":"3ce28a955c046dc69f37b25dc40cf1dbc954a5cf","tid":541840,"uid":25560,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:43:47.000Z","msg":"一對一床上教？"},{"pid":"1271bcff54939fc493e00c71faee9299947c36ba","tid":541840,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0abd4b767fa7bbdc853bc1b4b1e493eecf201ce5","tid":541840,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:42:38.000Z","msg":"推普廢粵<br />\n不了！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:54:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s10.postimg.org/6rb9q6xll/Sign_JPG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs10.postimg.org%2F6rb9q6xll%2FSign_JPG.jpg&h=86429792&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3eff8f0d571977bcb9c9e6775851cf4ba0ce26d7","tid":541840,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:57:03.000Z","msg":"咁你有無意欲留港？廣東話講成點？"},{"pid":"a84d187a2d8d9159fb1c56a304bf81e6e4246da7","tid":541840,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:58:04.000Z","msg":"補完都過唔到既話，條數點計？"},{"pid":"2c6fc40c81de4a23ad6f87d40a60feffa1f31b58","tid":541840,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:58:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>她接受傳媒訪問時稱普通話現在是國際語言，也是中國官方的語言。香港小學都設有普通話課，「所以大學都應該有的」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港官方語言係英文同粵語<br />\n<br />\n小學應該無, 有係錯誤"},{"pid":"bea241cf115cc14e39403a204ccfb21cca4545b7","tid":541840,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:59:19.000Z","msg":"高招 識玩"},{"pid":"99f0a3178e509e079d525496be80752a535cfde9","tid":541840,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:06:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>她接受傳媒訪問時稱普通話現在是國際語言</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係香港班無骨氣既賤種, 遷就班支那人去講蝗語<br />\n<br />\n令支那人認為蝗語係「國際語言」<br />\n<br />\n你唔撚遷就佢地, 係香港用唔撚到, 佢地咪無得UP句乜春「國際語言」囉！"},{"pid":"04611e3311c2b0674451a5428695b7477fd5cdb4","tid":541840,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:07:17.000Z","msg":"我教你法文"},{"pid":"589bee4dfbb71e0899dba78fcb40036e55a32fb7","tid":541840,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:07:59.000Z","msg":"真係俾人恰到上心口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aafd4c8c7b4e01d54965bc7efc52e55f5317f0a4","tid":541840,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:09:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>她接受傳媒訪問時稱普通話現在是國際語言</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nJETSTAR肯你班契弟賤種講蝗語先講乜春「國際語言」啦<br />\n<br />\n係香港人咁犯賤, 先會同蝗蟲講蝗話！<br />\n<br />\n================================================<br />\n<br />\n中國媒體報道指，前晚在日本東京成田機場中，有175名中國旅客因航班延誤，與當地警方爆發衝突，其間一度唱國歌。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，一班由成田飛往上海浦東的捷星日本航空航班，原定於前晚9時45分登機，但旅客卻一直滯留在T3航站樓，未獲安排登機。直至當晚10時15分左右，航空公司才廣播指，因為上海的天氣原因，航班將延遲24小時起飛。<br />\n<br />\n由於該航空公司在此後的24小時內沒有任何航班飛往上海，全機180名旅客滯留機場。隨後，航空公司帶走5名日本旅客，卻未有理會餘下的175名中國旅客，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">且拒絕安排會說中文的工作人員到場協助雙方溝通，只要求他們領走自己的行李，自行解決住宿等問題，還用英語說「get out（離開）」。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由於事發時間接近凌晨，在場175名中國旅客未能自行解決住宿及交通問題。他們要求捷星日本航空派出會中文的工作人員進行當面溝通；協助安排乘搭捷星日本航空的聯盟公司（日本航空）的航班；不能肆意切斷登機口這邊的電、暖氣和水；現場旅客中有長者、小孩、身體不適者，如發生突發狀況需給予醫療救助。不過，各項要求均被拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n凌晨2時許，有旅客欲前往離境區內的二樓購買食品，卻遭航空公司職員阻攔。旅客和在場的2名工作人員發生爭執，隨後爆發肢體衝突。航空公司職員隨即報警，1名乘客要求派中文繙譯在場，以配合警方調查，當時有警員要求立刻強行帶走他，其間，該乘客的衣服被扯爛。雙方爆發推撞，場面非常混亂。據現場影片所見，雙方當時互相推撞，有人突然唱出國歌。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，在中國大使館的出面督促下，滯留在成田國際機場的175名中國旅客隨後已接獲登機通知。"},{"pid":"6c5c8375abb5db52aad6efa403ad45c904919c2c","tid":541840,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"589bee4dfbb71e0899dba78fcb40036e55a32fb7","tid":541840,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:07:59.000Z","msg":"真係俾人恰到上心口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:13:02.000Z","msg":"港豬俾人恰到上心口, <br />\n<br />\n仲要同蝗蟲講蝗語<br />\n<br />\n係咪犯賤？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s10.postimg.org/6rb9q6xll/Sign_JPG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs10.postimg.org%2F6rb9q6xll%2FSign_JPG.jpg&h=86429792&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f64d5d0e233c6eb9b18a7d2a1a4fc4a7426d52b","tid":541840,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:16:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_RUqqa0dH9wY/TFUMoSC8sjI/AAAAAAAACqQ/joa3ETf3twg/s1600/diunama.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F_RUqqa0dH9wY%2FTFUMoSC8sjI%2FAAAAAAAACqQ%2Fjoa3ETf3twg%2Fs1600%2Fdiunama.jpg&h=ca438812&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82f8188d14998db8a3c1853eac12799ee07ac43f","tid":541840,"uid":164914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:22:21.000Z","msg":"學普通話唔係問題，但係無必要硬性規定成為必修科囉，留翻比有興趣/有需要嘅人讀好過，咁先唔會浪費資源"},{"pid":"7c16b7238a30dbefcd34fd8ae9efb93d3147429e","tid":541840,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:23:42.000Z","msg":"而家講到因為浸大生成績差而反咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢都得既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d604442093b36843444f663334b695e0c14039","tid":541840,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82f8188d14998db8a3c1853eac12799ee07ac43f","tid":541840,"uid":164914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:22:21.000Z","msg":"學普通話唔係問題，但係無必要硬性規定成為必修科囉，留翻比有興趣/有需要嘅人讀好過，咁先唔會浪費資源"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:24:50.000Z","msg":"中學都唔係必修科去到大學竟然必考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全世界有咩制度咁荒謬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e72eeb2622845ecc89f85184e7d4a7bf94a4a1b5","tid":541840,"uid":2404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:28:35.000Z","msg":"推英廢普<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127264c9d8e5f8b6710d7ad2bf2a40cdcece4f62","tid":541840,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:32:34.000Z","msg":"返去偉大嘅祖國奶呀爺鞋，食你嘅地溝油ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddac0cf4cb3c6e24cc7488e16bb4deb8189173b5","tid":541840,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a6bb5d33aa65d96ddffd99109e68b1347dbcc0","tid":541840,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:36:30.000Z","msg":"復興嶺南文化"}]}